column2: SELECT sg.galaxy_id, sg.ra as ra_i, s.ra, sg.dec as dec_i, s.dec, n.objid, n.distance * #. as distance, log1# (n.distance * #.) as log_distance, s.z, s.zErr, s.velDisp, s.velDispErr, s.snMedian, l.sigmaStars, l.sigmaStarsErr, l.chisq, l.bpt, l.EW_Hb_#, l.EW_Hb_#_Err, l.Flux_Hb_#, l.Flux_Hb_#_Err, l.Flux_Cont_Hb_#, l.Flux_Cont_Hb_#_Err, l.EW_Ha_#, l.EW_Ha_#_Err, l.Flux_Ha_#, l.Flux_Ha_#_Err, l.Flux_Cont_Ha_#, l.Flux_Cont_Ha_#_Err, l.V_Ha_#, l.V_Ha_#_Err, l.Sigma_Ha_#, l.Sigma_Ha_#_Err INTO mydb.sdss7groups_kinematics FROM MyDB.sdss7groups AS sg CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (sg.ra, sg.dec, #) AS n JOIN SpecObj AS s ON n.objid = s.bestobjid JOIN emissionLinesPort as l ON s.specobjid = l.specobjid
